703
00:42:34,465 --> 00:42:37,798
- Come back here, you! Robbie!
- You're gonna kill me!

704
00:42:37,869 --> 00:42:40,531
- I got you now.
- Let me go!

705
00:42:40,605 --> 00:42:43,574
- I got you. There's your Dad.
- Hey, what's goin' on?

706
00:42:43,641 --> 00:42:47,236
- Get out of here!
- It's a reaction to the mysolene.

707
00:42:47,311 --> 00:42:50,405
- Get out of here!
- Will you be still?
Look at Daddy's truck.

708
00:42:50,481 --> 00:42:53,109
- Let me go, you pig! I hate you!
- Ohhh!

709
00:42:53,184 --> 00:42:56,711
Hey, don't you ever talk to your mother
like that! Do you hear me? Ohh!

710
00:42:56,787 --> 00:43:00,518
- [Robbie Crying]
- Oh, no! Oh, honey.

711
00:43:00,591 --> 00:43:02,855
Come on.
Somebody help me, please!

712
00:43:02,927 --> 00:43:06,385
Somebody help us!
Oh, it's okay.

713
00:43:06,464 --> 00:43:10,400
