[Children Playing,
Chattering]

804
00:49:18,736 --> 00:49:20,670
Hi.

805
00:49:22,199 --> 00:49:26,602
Oh, I... probably average
three or four seizures a month.

806
00:49:26,670 --> 00:49:30,367
Be better if they restricted themselves
to weekends and holidays.

807
00:49:30,441 --> 00:49:33,604
[Laughs]
Yeah.

808
00:49:33,677 --> 00:49:37,477
Um, when I was
in elementary school...

809
00:49:37,548 --> 00:49:42,542
I was on so much medicine,
the other kids assumed I was retarded.

810
00:49:42,620 --> 00:49:47,284
I had a seizure during
our fourth grade talent show.

811
00:49:47,358 --> 00:49:53,160
They must have thought I was doing
my impression of a fried egg.

812
00:49:53,230 --> 00:49:56,666
Not too many kids wanted to
play with me after that.

813
00:49:56,734 --> 00:50:01,797
Took my parents weeks
to go back into public.

814
00:50:04,041 --> 00:50:06,236
Later on, I got to
where I could...

815
00:50:06,310 --> 00:50:09,245
...tell a couple minutes
in advance when one was coming.

816
00:50:09,313 --> 00:50:13,010
I get auras.
Things start to change colors.

817
00:50:13,083 --> 00:50:15,244
My head aches.

818
00:50:15,319 --> 00:50:18,618
I try to hide it at work. I don't wanna
lose my medical insurance...

819
00:50:18,689 --> 00:50:20,623
...or worse, my job.

820
00:50:20,691 --> 00:50:22,556
Can't drive.

821
00:50:25,195 --> 00:50:30,531
My marriage broke up because
the drugs keep me from being
a normal lover.

822
00:50:30,601 --> 00:50:35,595
And I seize in my sleep,
I cuss, I make animal noises.

823
00:50:38,342 --> 00:50:42,005
There is anger and loneliness.

824
00:50:42,079 --> 00:50:45,947
But when the self-pity comes,
I try to say to myself...

825
00:50:46,016 --> 00:50:48,951
,,,instead of,
"What life do I have?"...

826
00:50:50,554 --> 00:50:53,022
..."What life can I build?"

827
00:50:58,729 --> 00:51:00,663
Then who did take it down?

828
00:51:00,731 --> 00:51:02,665
I don't know.
What are you blaming me for?

829
00:51:02,733 --> 00:51:05,827
Because it's a criminal offense
to remove a foreclosure notice.
You can go to jail.

830
00:51:05,903 --> 00:51:08,633
