it and you're gonna put it back.

831
00:51:08,706 --> 00:51:11,140
Fine. You want me to say
I took it down? I took it down.

832
00:51:11,208 --> 00:51:14,541
Then put it back.

833
00:51:14,611 --> 00:51:17,409
- How come you're always
pickin' on me lately?
- I'm not pickin' on you.

834
00:51:17,481 --> 00:51:19,915
