I said. I was just mad.

838
00:51:26,924 --> 00:51:29,290
What are you talkin' about?

839
00:51:29,360 --> 00:51:31,954
Oh, right. Like Mom
didn't tell you.

840
00:51:32,029 --> 00:51:34,623
