1316
01:27:54,643 --> 01:27:56,634
Come on! Hurry up!

1317
01:27:56,711 --> 01:27:59,271
- Do you see him anywhere?
- I don't see him.

1318
01:28:06,121 --> 01:28:08,555
See him?

1319
01:28:08,623 --> 01:28:10,648
Hey, squirt!

1320
01:28:10,725 --> 01:28:13,125
Good goin',
but you need to hang on.

1321
01:28:13,194 --> 01:28:15,958
I don't need to. I'm big!

1322
01:28:18,300 --> 01:28:20,268
Gotcha!

1323
01:28:24,105 --> 01:28:27,404
Hey, Margeen, look at me!

1324
01:28:27,475 --> 01:28:30,205
[Margeen]
Ride 'em, cowboy!

1325
01:28:32,981 --> 01:28:34,915
